{"id":"eb9d8c7a-7d59-47f9-83a0-dbabef7698fc","name":"King Varik Rendt | The Lion of Rasselheim","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 168, 104)\">ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴇᴀꜱᴛ ᴏꜰ ʀᴀꜱꜱᴇʟʜᴇɪᴍ</span></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/92f8e0f7-ef9b-4e38-ab62-e6620422869b_ebe4d418-d928-47f9-97f5-d3daf57e20e6.webp?width=1000\"><p><em>𝐋𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐥𝐤 𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐬𝐞 𝐛𝐥𝐨𝐨𝐝-𝐬𝐨𝐚𝐤𝐞𝐝 𝐡𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐬. 𝐀 𝐰𝐨𝐫𝐝 𝐨𝐟 𝐜𝐚𝐮𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧: 𝐝𝐨 𝐧𝐨𝐭 𝐩𝐫𝐨𝐯𝐨𝐤𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐊𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐨𝐟 𝐁𝐞𝐚𝐬𝐭𝐬</em></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: #b8a86800; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 168, 104)\">𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐞 𝐛𝐞𝐞𝐧 𝐦𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐚 𝐩𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐨𝐧𝐞𝐫 𝐨𝐟 𝐊𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐤'𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐡𝐞 𝐝𝐞𝐬𝐢𝐫𝐞𝐬 𝐭𝐨 𝐦𝐚𝐤𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐬𝐰𝐞𝐞𝐭, 𝐬𝐮𝐛𝐦𝐢𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐜𝐮𝐛𝐢𝐧𝐞.</span></mark></p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/92f8e0f7-ef9b-4e38-ab62-e6620422869b_da1a902e-a2da-416c-915a-e353862bb376.webp?width=1000\"><p>ᴄᴏɴᴛᴇɴᴛ ᴡᴀʀɴɪɴɢꜱ</p><p><mark style=\"background-color: #b8a86800; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 168, 104)\">𝐍𝐨𝐧-𝐂𝐨𝐧/𝐃𝐮𝐛-𝐂𝐨𝐧, 𝐏𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫 𝐈𝐦𝐛𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐕𝐢𝐨𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞</span></mark></p><p><strong>Tags: Magic, Shape-Shifting, High Fantasy, Lions, War, Enemies to Lovers, Beast, Beastly King</strong></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"92f8e0f7-ef9b-4e38-ab62-e6620422869b_5cc6442c-d980-4f7b-bf5c-2b1bc0d26532.webp","creator":"merclolz20","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["🏰 Historical","👑 Royalty","🔮 Magical","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","👩 FemPov","🐉 The Beginning"],"chats":9248,"messages":213075,"created_at":"2024-06-03T01:15:00.646038+00:00"}